Landslide in Western Rwanda Kills 13 Members of Same Family, RNA Reports

-- B y   B r i a n   L a t h a m
-- 
2011-05-13T10:41:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-13/landslide-in-western-rwanda-kills-13-members-of-same-family-rna-reports.html
A landslide in western  Rwanda  killed
13 people, all members of the same family,  Rwanda News Agency 
said, citing Angela Mukaminani, deputy mayor for the district.  An unidentified man, along with his three wives and their
children, were crushed in the landslide after a section of
hillside collapsed earlier today, the Kigali-based  news agency 
said. Nine bodies have so far been recovered, RNA said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brian Latham in Johannesburg at 
 blatham@bloomberg.net   To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Gordon Bell at   gbell16@bloomberg.net  